OL,3,CBoy, 14, charged with terror offence
OL,4,Cafter alleged plans to target two
OL,5,Cmosques
OL,7,FA 14-year-old boy has been charged
OL,8,Fwith an offence linked to "extreme
OL,9,Fright-wing terrorism" after police
OL,10,Fdiscovered an alleged plan to target
OL,11,Ftwo London mosques.
OL,13,FThe child was initially arrested at an
OL,14,Faddress on suspicion of criminal
OL,15,Fdamage to a vehicle, but officers
OL,16,Fsearching the location found "a number
OL,17,Fof documents of concern", the
OL,18,FMetropolitan Police said.
OL,26,@pD@[OUqD@UO]xD@^OUyD@XO]
