PN,31202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1784184477
OL,3,CBoy, 14, charged with terror offence
OL,4,Cafter alleged plans to target two
OL,5,Cmosques
OL,7,FHe is accused of planning to target
OL,8,Fthe two places of worship in Sutton,
OL,9,Fsouth London, which are both being
OL,10,Fsupported by specialist officers.
OL,12,FThe boy, who was arrested in the south
OL,13,FLondon area, has been charged with
OL,14,Fpreparation of terrorist acts on or
OL,15,Fbefore July 9, as well as racially
OL,16,Faggravated damage to property by
OL,17,Fallegedly damaging a car window on or
OL,18,Fbefore June 20, the force said.
