OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1784184477
OL,3,CBoy, 14, charged with terror offence
OL,4,Cafter alleged plans to target two
OL,5,Cmosques
OL,7,FDetective Chief Superintendent Nick
OL,8,FBlackburn, in charge of local policing
OL,9,Ffor the south London area, said:
OL,10,F"These charges come just days after 12
OL,11,Fpeople were arrested for a suspected
OL,12,Fthreat to an Islamic festival in
OL,13,FSuffolk and a man was arrested for an
OL,14,Falleged assault outside a mosque in
OL,15,FLeyton."
OL,17,FHe added: "We should not underestimate
OL,18,Fthe cumulative impact of incidents of
OL,19,Fthis nature on the Muslim community."
OL,26,@rD@AOUwD@HO]yD@KOU{D@eO]
