CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1784184477
OL,3,CBoy, 14, charged with terror offence
OL,4,Cafter alleged plans to target two
OL,5,Cmosques
OL,7,FThe child, who cannot be named because
OL,8,Fof his age, has been remanded in
OL,9,Fcustody and will appear at Westminster
OL,10,FMagistrates' Court on Thursday.
OL,12,FCommander Helen Flanagan, head of
OL,13,FCounter Terrorism Policing (CTP)
OL,14,FLondon, said they are seeing an
OL,15,Fincreasing number of children and
OL,16,Fyoung people in their casework.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
