PN,31206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1784184477
OL,3,CBoy, 14, charged with terror offence
OL,4,Cafter alleged plans to target two
OL,5,Cmosques
OL,7,FIn a statement issued by the Met, she
OL,8,Fsaid: "This is a very serious
OL,9,Fterrorism charge against a young boy
OL,10,Fand likely to be highly concerning to
OL,11,Fthe public and the local community.
OL,13,F"We know this will be particularly
OL,14,Fconcerning to the Muslim community and
OL,15,Fwe are working closely with the venues
OL,16,Faffected to ensure they are kept
OL,17,Fupdated and to provide advice, support
OL,18,Fand reassurance, and this will
OL,19,Fcontinue."
OL,26,@pD@GOUuD@AOU{D@JO]
