OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1784184477
OL,3,CBoy, 14, charged with terror offence
OL,4,Cafter alleged plans to target two
OL,5,Cmosques
OL,7,FPolice have increased patrols in
OL,8,Faffected areas, and the Met is working
OL,9,Fclosely with counter-terror police on
OL,10,Fthe investigation.
OL,12,FThere is not believed to be "any
OL,13,Fenduring or wider threat" ` and police
OL,14,Fare not seeking anyone else in
OL,15,Fconnection with the incidents, the Met
OL,16,Fadded.
OL,18,FThis is a breaking story, more to
OL,19,Ffollow
OL,26,@tD@]OUuD@YO]
